I"b<p>There are some places that are unforgettable; places that make the kind of impact in your memory so that just a smell or sound can instantly transport you back there. Casa Ellul, one of the original boutique hotels in Valletta, is such a place. I had the pleasure of staying there recently and I am still enchanted.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/casa-ellul/casa-ellul-6.jpg" alt="casa-ellul-6.jpg" /></p>

<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
